Plintissa continued walking toward the Pred base...she stopped and looked
behind her to see if anyone was following to apoligize......she seen no
one......she continued on the give the Preds the codes, seeing as she had no
more position with the Maximals, since she didn't want to work with an
incompetent leader like Liono.....she coughed and spit out the other
chip.....she remembered what Suukie did to her and growled......she
continued to walk on......hoping Iron raptor could forgive her for what she
must now do......

> ( Actually, believe it or not Dinobot's just come out of a CR chamber in
the base after Tavatron dragged him there and Ramhorn is being dragged to a
CR chamber by a few fembots. So I have no clue who Prowl is looking at.
Sorry.)
>
> * Zyber trotted out of Rowdy's cave and began to sniff around for the
plants and herds she needed to heal Striker, she kept her nose to the ground
and soon came up with the sent of pond lily. She smiled as she began to
follow it's sent.
> Soon Zyber cane to a shallow pond and looked into it's waters, there was
lily there but half of it was submerged. She sighed as she waded into the
pond and took a few of the soft white flowers from the pads.
> She walked out of the pond and shook every limb in turn until she was sure
that they were not soaking wet. Now it was time to find what she needed
most...devil's club.*
>
> _________________________________________________
>
> * Iron Raptor exited the Ark and looked up at the damage when Prowl
mentioned it.*
>
> " I've got the ship's repair system working on that right now, it'll take
a few mega-cycles but it'll be done."
>
> * She then looked at Prowl and smiled.*
>
> " Don't worry, it'll be complete before the next attack."
>
> * Iron Raptor then looked out at the scene before her and sighed, smoking
craters and blast areas...a typical battle field. She took a few steps
forward and scanned, her scanners picked up a stray signature heading
towards the Predacon base. They indicated that the signature was that of
Plintissa's, but why would she be going to the Pred base willingly?
> Iron Raptor looked back at Prowl with concern.*
>
> " I've got a stray signature on my screen here, I think that it's
Plintissa but why would she be going to the Pred base?"
>
